Vet Nick Fisher, 31, from Leintwardine, Shropshire, said his bedlington lurcher was left behaving strangely after eating the drugs he found at a bus stop .
The four-year-old hound seemed to think he was being chased and had dilated pupils and bloodshot eyes .
But after 45 minutes of drooling at the mouth uncontrollably, he seemed back to normal following his 'trip'